## Overview

This dashboard provides an Overview of Symantec Endpoint Security through visualizations. It includes Events Categorized by Severity, Operating System Type, and Demonstrates Event Types over Time. Additionally, it showcases Event Status, Feature Name, Environment, Logging Device IP, Device Edition, and Device Type. Furthermore, it displays the Count of Personal Devices and breaks down Events by Product and Device Manufacturer. Lastly, it highlights the Top 10 Device Domains, Top 10 Event Types, and Top 10 Source and Destination IPs.
